divs: Sighting Detailsmy mate and i were at the beach watching the waves to see if it was any good for surfing and i took 4 photos on my nokia E71 phone camera.. the interesting photo is the 2nd photo taken, i have no idea wat it is or could be, it dosnt look like a plane or a bird, and i didnt see it when i took the picture, i only realised something was there when i got home and had a look on my computer... i cant even try to guess its size or speed, and i cant find a shadow to try work out how far away it is.. the sun was to my left and i would have been facing almost directly east... please let me know wat u think..
